Download the CPI series in long format

get_ipc_long.Rd

Download the CPI inflacion series for the Dominican Republic in any disaggregation

Usage

get_ipc_long(
  desagregacion = c("general", "grupo", "subgrupo", "clase", "subclase", "articulo")
)

Arguments

desagregacion

string with the desired disaggregation. options: "general", "grupo", "subgrupo", "clase", "subclase", "articulo"

Value

a tibble

Examples

get_ipc_long("general")
